p: \rWell, well, well. Look who it is!
\rThe hero who single-handedly shut down the Abyssal Cult.
\rI have to admit: that's very impressive.
\rYou have my thanks, on behalf of everyone in this town.
\rThe storms faded away, and we cleared the streets of all the water.
\rEverything looks like it's going to be all right.
\rBut let's not keep you waiting any longer!
\rYou came for a Gym Battle, right?
\rAllow me to introduce myself, you know, officially.
\rMy name is Anastasia- the leader of the Kepler City Gym.
\rThe theme of my Gym is machinery- as such, I specialize in Steel- and Electric-types.
\rI have to admit, I'm pretty excited for this battle.
\rI mean, it's not every day you get to beat someone who dismantled a cult!
\rMy Pokemon work together like the gears in a machine!
\rYou might have beaten Audrey, \pn... but you won't Faraday against me!
pbTrainerBattle(PBTrainers::LEADER_Anastasia,"Anastasia",_I("Don't get too excited, you'll change state!"),false,0)
\rIt's standard to give a TM too, right? Here you are!
\rThunderbolt is an important move for any Pokemon trainer.\nIt's the generic Electric-type move that always has a use.
\rI'm off to work on a side project.\nI'll be in my workshop under the Gym if you need me.
\rJust don't come in for a while. I'm working on something... private.
Battle: \bI'm a master of machines and electricity. You don't stand a chance!
\bI'm a master of machines and electricity. You don't stand a chance!
Battle: \rElectric-type Pokemon are the strongest of all!
EndSpeech: Hmph! I'm not a liar!
\rElectric-type Pokemon are the strongest of all!
Battle: \bI'd wish you luck against Anastasia, but I don't think you'll even make it to her!
EndSpeech: Well, evidently I need to reconsider my theory.
EndBattle: \bWell, evidently I need to reconsider my theory.
\bI'd wish you luck against Anastasia, but I don't think you'll even make it to her!

\bWell, evidently I need to reconsider my theory.
Battle: \rHave you ever considered becoming a scientist?
EndSpeech: It's super interesting and fun! I recommend it!
EndBattle: \rIt's super interesting and fun! I recommend it!
\rHave you ever considered becoming a scientist?
pbTrainerBattle(PBTrainers::SCIENTIST_F,"Curie",_I("It's super interesting and fun! I recommend it!"),false,0)
\rIt's super interesting and fun! I recommend it!
\bI heard you took down the Abyssal Cult, champ!
\bThat's incredible! I knew you had it in you!
\bIndeed, but don't get too cocky, now!
\bShe has a machine-themed Gym, and she specializes in both Steel- and Electric-types!
\bNicely done, champ, I can't believe you beat Anastasia! Great work!
